profile: Interested in quality stone and brick installations? Cliffside Masonry prides itself on the quality and dexterity of our installations. profile: A & K Stone Masonry Ltd has been serving as a leading masonry contractor for over 24 years within Calgary and surrounding areas. I love the work that I do, and have taken a special interest in natural and artificial stone, as well as brick projects. As a fully-certified professional, I’m ready to tackle anything from the most complex and large scale construction projects to the smallest of repair jobs. I’m driven by my commitment to excellence and will go the extra mile to make sure my clients are completely satisfied with my work. I look forward to discussing your specific project needs.
